headline: Expedia (EXPE): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q1 Earnings?
summary: Expedia trades at $171.01 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, losing 7.4% over the last six months while the S&P 500 is down 2.5%. This was partly driven by its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
